@DATABASE "Virus Info Base"
@NODE MAIN "Jeff Butonic 3.00"
     Name         : Jeff Butonic 3.00

     Aliases      : No Aliases

     Clone        : No Clones

     Type/size    : File/2916

     Symptoms     : Shows an alert

     Discovered   : 01-06-91

     Way to infect: File infection

     Rating       : Less Dangerous

     Kickstarts   : 1.2/1.3/2.0 BUT: only DD-Disks !!!

     Damage       : No Damage

     Removal      : Delete file. 

     Comments     : When you are starting the JeffV3.00 virus it
                    first decodes itself with a eor-loop.
                    Then it changes the Kick-Vectors and patches
                    the DoIO()-Vector from the exec.library.
                    The DoIO()-Vector is used to infect other disks.
                    If you are inserting an unprotected disk, the
                    virus scans the root-block of it ($6E000 = only
                    DD-Disks!!!) and tries to create the virusfile
                    and to modifiy the startup-sequence. No DOS-functions
                    are used (!!). 

                    Sometimes the window-title change and the following
                    messages will appear:
        
        Ich brauch jetzt Alk'!
        Bitte keinen Wodka!Stau auf Datenbus bei Speicherkilometer 128!
        Mehr Buszyklen fŁr den Prozessor!
        Ein dreifach MITLEID fŁr Atari ST!
        ©89 by BUTONIC
        PC/XT: Spendenkonto 004...
        Freiheit fŁr den Tastaturprozessor!
        C fŁr Looser
        Paula meint, Agnus sei zu dick.
        Die CPU braucht etwas SchmierŲl
        C64 - jetzt mit Pampers im 3erPack
        JEFF=ungefšhrlich+schŁtzt vor Viren

                   Depending of $DFF006 , the virus gives out an alert:

                          Hi.
                 JEFF's speaking here...
               (w) by the genious BUTONIC.
